ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would not recommend this course but unfortunately it is a required course.
We don't have a choice anyway...
As mentioned above, there were some very good talks in it. I would recommend it to another student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: In addition to learning about biology as a whole, it was also amazing to realize how much progress one has made from one year to the next.
This course did not help or contribute to my research.
In more than on case I got an idea important for my work from the work being presented.
By hearing what others in the department are working on, I learned more about the various fields od study in our department, as well as gained new insight on doing research, troubleshooting, etc.
